### === ADMIN 계정 준비 ===

### 0-1. ADMIN용 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "admin1234",
  "nickname": "관리자"
}

### 0-2. DB에서 role을 ADMIN으로 변경 (MySQL 콘솔에서 실행)
# docker exec auth-board-mysql mysql -uauth_user -puser1234 auth_board -e "UPDATE member SET role='ADMIN' WHERE email='admin@test.com';"

### 0-3. ADMIN 로그인 → accessToken 복사
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "admin1234"
}

### === 관리자 API 테스트 ===

